{"tid":555874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PM2.5空氣污染預警 中國又污染世界空氣","createTime":"2018-02-10T02:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T02:54:46.000Z","uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"470bd16412539d571f889aeeca29347415be0497","tid":555874,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T02:49:40.000Z","msg":"睇番條等壓線, 成個華中都冇乜風, 大量污染物正在累積<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.windy.com/?27.508,112.939,5,i:pressure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.windy.com%2F%3F27.508%2C112.939%2C5%2Ci%3Apressure&d=9kWRrrbm%2Fk7%2Bxn%2BO0qEwoAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f204f438\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.windy.com/?27.508,112.939,5,i:pressure</a><br />\n<br />\n山東半島自1月底長期999爆錶, 污染物開始吹去朝鮮半島, 南韓就瀨嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/dDfQAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FdDfQAa.jpg&h=5888d78d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本仔嘅預測係2月11日香港嘅PM2.5值將會到達最高點, 好大機會係嗰日有季候風補充抵達, 順便將污染物帶過嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pm25.jp/yosoku/parts/casu/180209/29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpm25.jp%2Fyosoku%2Fparts%2Fcasu%2F180209%2F29.png&h=fa0ffdf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個參考醬油<br />\n<a href=\"http://aqicn.org/forecast/asia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faqicn.org%2Fforecast%2Fasia%2F&d=9kWRrrbm%2Fk7%2Bxn%2BO0qEwoAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=df42f9e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://aqicn.org/forecast/asia/</a>"},{"pid":"86f510f35845b78bc51bf7198cfb775917c54cc8","tid":555874,"uid":42042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}